# Operator runtime state (per-machine, mutated at runtime — must never be committed)
# Trailing * covers the .bak sibling too: the rule used to name the .graphml exactly, so
# knowledge_graph.graphml.bak (a byte-identical copy of the ignored graph) was left untracked but
# NOT ignored — one `git add -A` from being committed.
agent/layla/memory/knowledge_graph.graphml*
*.graphml.bak
